Detailed Description

cvmx_mio_emm_dma_fifo_adr

This register specifies the internal address that is loaded into the eMMC internal DMA FIFO. The FIFO is used to queue up operations for the MIO_EMM_DMA_CFG/MIO_EMM_DMA_ADR when the DMA completes successfully.
